            <a href="http://www.viget.com/inspire/refresh-dc-november-2010-recap-designing-for-one-billion-people/">Refresh DC November 2010 Recap: Designing for One Billion People</a>            </h2>
                        <div class="inner_post">

<div class="author_pic jgarber">

<a class="url" href="/about/team/jgarber" title="Jason Garber"><img alt="Jason Garber" class="photo" src="/images/inspire/author_image_frame.png" width="112" height="105" /></a></div>




