                                <p><a href="http://refresh-dc.org/">Refresh DC</a> returned in a big way a week before the Thanksgiving holiday with a top-notch talk on "Designing for One Billion People."</p>

<p><a href="http://clearspring.com/">Clearspring's</a> Director of User Experience, Jim Lane, spoke on a number of topics relating to how his company tackled design challenges at tremendous scale. Clearspring builds and supports the <a href="http://www.addthis.com/">AddThis</a> sharing platform and currently serves 2 billion share button views <em>every single day</em>.</p>                                                                            <p><strong><a href="/inspire/refresh-dc-november-2010-recap-designing-for-one-billion-people#continue">Continue reading "Refresh DC November 2010 Recap: Designing for One Billion People"</a></strong></p>                           
                                                   
