<div id="comments" class="divider"><h3>Recent Comments</h3>
        
<div id="big_comment">

	<p>Great write up Mindy!&nbsp; I noticed some of the same politics when working with high school web sites, though to a much lesser scale thank goodness.
</p>
<p>
Great work on the Lafeyette site too!
</p>...
